# ── IP — factor models, weights, backtests (LOCAL ONLY, never commit) ────────
# Factor IP lives in MFC/IP/ (subfolder); runner/ holds local-only operator
# tools. git refuses to track anything under either path so the IP can never
# accidentally end up on the public GitHub repo. The bare shared/ and
# strategies/ entries are a belt-and-suspenders guard in case files ever get
# moved back to the root.
IP/
runner/
shared/
strategies/
screener_local/

# ── Secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env

# ── Python cache ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/

# ── macOS system files ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*
Thumbs.db

# ── Jupyter ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.ipynb

# ── Generated outputs (re-runnable; large PNGs and CSVs not needed in git) ───
strategies/*/outputs/*.png
strategies/*/outputs/*.csv

# ── Excel lock files ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
~$*.xlsx
~$*.xls

# ── Virtual environments ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
venv/
.venv/
env/
.env_dir/

# ── IDE / editor ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
